WEBVTT

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:03.599
if due to bad investments or family
disputes he has little money,

00:03:03.600 --> 00:03:06.119
he still has to have a fancy car.

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:11.799
For my brother’s education abroad,
my mother had to pawn her jewelery,

00:03:11.800 --> 00:03:15.479
and my father invested
all his money through me.

00:03:15.480 --> 00:03:17.617
One person went to the extent
of telling him:

00:03:17.617 --> 00:03:19.647
"You should have bought her gold instead."

00:03:19.647 --> 00:03:21.999
My father replied,

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:24.639
“Gold should be within her,

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:26.799
what will she do with gold outside?

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:30.319
A gold medalist has gold
within, not outside.